    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-11-30T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-11-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="563"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d563">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Springer</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-11-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 30, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Superior court Matanzas, session 24th instant, to decide competency between civil
                    and military jurisdiction for the cognizance of the case reported in my dispatch
                    No. 205, has decided in favor of military jurisdiction.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Springer.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
